    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera is a mechanically robust example of the 3.6L M96 flat-six, featuring VarioCam Plus for an optimized torque curve. Crucially, the IMS bearing has been retrofitted with a dual-row ceramic solution, and the rear main seal (RMS) was replaced concurrently. Power is managed via a G96 6-speed manual transaxle, delivering linear acceleration to the rear wheels. The suspension has been refreshed with Bilstein B6 dampers and high-durometer bushings, maintaining factory geometry while sharpening turn-in. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain is in peak operational state, offering the visceral, analog feedback desired by purists.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
