      "description": "This 2016 Lexus RX 350 is the perfect blend of luxury and dependability. Finished in a timeless Nebula Gray Pearl, the exterior remains vibrant with only minor, expected road wear consistent with careful ownership. Inside, the Parchment leather interior has been meticulously maintained; it is smoke-free and shows only light softening on the driver\u2019s bolster. Every feature, from the premium surround-sound system to the heated steering wheel, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle is sound, boasting a complete service history from authorized dealerships. Recent maintenance includes a fresh synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection confirming the brakes and tires are in excellent shape for the miles ahead. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next long-term owner.",
