      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? This car has been so good to me and is in wonderful shape, inside and out. It drives smoothly and has been well-loved, making it the perfect companion for your daily commutes or weekend road trips. I'm sad to see it go, but I know it'll make its next owner very happy! Come by and take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
