      "description": "This BMW M3 (E46) is a mechanically sorted driver\u2019s car featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. The powertrain delivers linear torque and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline, mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. To ensure long-term reliability, the VANOS system has been professionally serviced, and the rear subframe has been reinforced\u2014a critical proactive measure for this chassis. The limited-slip differential remains tight, providing excellent traction through corners, while the suspension geometry is preserved with refreshed bushings. This is a performance-first example with the mechanical pedigree to match its legendary reputation.",
